Taron Trump a Yammacin Virginia, Tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara yakin neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia a daren yau.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko na jerin kamfen biyar na Trump da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, tare da Tennessee da Mississippi, inda ya tsaya a wurare masu kyau.
An sake wa'adin zaben da ake yi a Kotun Koli, domin Trump ya samu goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba, saboda jam'iyyar Republican na iya rasa rinjaye a majalisar.
A wane lokaci ne za a fara yakin neman zaben Trump a Virginia ta Yamma a yau kuma a ina za a iya kallon sa a yanar gizo?
An shirya taron yakin neman zaben Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, a ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018, da karfe bakwai na yamma a lokacin Kudu.
Za ku iya kallon yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia a yanzu a YouTube.
Trump zai iya yin magana game da sauraron kotun koli a wannan makon game da nadin Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka jinkirta har mako guda yayin da ake jiran binciken FBI game da zargin fyade.
Amma babban burin wannan yakin shine don taimakawa jam'iyyar Republican ta samu wani ci gaba a zaben Nuwamba.
Wannan ya ba wa masu goyon bayan Trump damar gudanar da yakin neman zabe guda biyar a mako mai zuwa, yayin da jam'iyyar Republican ke kokarin kara rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, in ji Reuters.
"Mafi yawan majalisa muhimmiyar manufa ce ga shugaban kasa, kuma yana tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai iya, saboda muna fuskantar yanayi mai wahala", in ji sakataren yakin neman zaben Trump, amma ya ki bayyana sunansa ga Reuters.
Taron na yau da ake sa ran za a yi a filin wasa na Wesbank Arena a Wheeling zai iya jawo magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma zai iya jan hankalin labarai daga Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump ya sake zuwa jihar West Virginia a watan da ya gabata, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da aka kada a 2016.
Trump yana son ya taimaka wa dan takararsa na Republican a majalisar dattijai na West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya ragu kadan.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ya taimaka", in ji Simon Heather, masanin kimiyya a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
