Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo zai kirkiro sabuwar yanar gizo don Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, yana shirin kafa wani kamfani da zai yi gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikin da aka yi kwanan nan daga wani almara na fasaha, Inrupt, wani kamfani ne wanda aka gina a kan wani dandamali mai budewa mai suna Berners-Lee Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanda za su iya samun damar su.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee yayi dariya cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce mamayar duniya.
"Dole ne mu yi haka yanzu", in ji shi game da wannan farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Wannan app yana amfani da fasaha mai ƙarfi wanda ke taimaka wa mutane su ƙirƙiri nasu "tushen bayanan kan layi" ko POD.
Yana ɗauke da jerin sunayen abokan aiki, jerin ayyuka, kalandar aiki, laburaren waƙa, da kuma wasu kayayyakin aiki na kai da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna aiki a lokaci guda a cikin mai bincike guda.
Abin da ke da ban mamaki game da ajiyar kan layi na sirri shi ne cewa yana dogara ne akan mai amfani wanda zai iya samun damar yin amfani da bayanai.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "karfafa mutum ta hanyar masu imani".
A cewar John Bruce, shugaban kamfanin, babban burin Inrupt shi ne samar da albarkatu, matakai da basira don sa kowa ya sami damar amfani da Solid.
Yanzu kamfani ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, da kuma wasu masu shirye-shirye na ma'aikata da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shirye masu sa kai waɗanda aka ƙulla su yi aiki a kan aikin.
Daga wannan makon, masu fasaha a ko'ina cikin duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da ba a haɗa su ba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa "ba su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da yin wani abu da zai canza tsarin kasuwancin su nan take.
"Ba mu taɓa tambayar su ba".
A wata sanarwa da aka buga a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "manufa ta Inrupt ita ce samar da wutar lantarki da tsarin halittu na kasuwanci don taimakawa kare daidaito da ingancin sabon hanyar sadarwa da aka gina a Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza Intanet lokacin da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a MIT.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ta kasance babbar murya a cikin muhawara ta tsaka tsaki a yanar gizo.
Bayan ya fara gudanar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee ya ci gaba da zama mai kafa da kuma darektan kungiyar World Wide Web Consortium, Internet Foundation da kuma Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan zamani na gaba na Intanet", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: Wani mai wa'azi a cikin Ikilisiyar Victoria a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya
