Mickelson ya rasa kwalliyarsa a gasar Ryder ta ranar Asabar
Ba'amurke Phil Mickelson ya kafa sabon tarihi a wasansa na Ryder Cup na 47 a ranar Lahadi, amma ya bukaci ya sake samun ƙoshin lafiya don ya ci gaba da tseren.
Mickelson ya shiga gasar shekara biyu a shekara ta 12, kuma a wasan Asabar, kyaftin Jim Furyk ya dakatar da shi har abada.
Mai nasara sau biyar, wanda a kullum yana cikin hankalin jama'a a Amurka, ya yi amfani da ranar yana mai goyon baya da kuma aiki a kan wasan a filin wasa don gyara kuskurensa.
