Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da aikata ta'addanci a birnin New York
Ofishin lauya na tarayya a New York yana neman hukuncin kisa wanda ba a taba yi ba tun 1953 ga wani laifi na tarayya, Saifullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya a watan Oktoba don shirya wani hari a kan hanyar keke a yankin West na Lower Manhattan, inda ya kai ga masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawa keke.
A cikin wata sanarwa da aka bayar a gundumar kudu ta birnin New York, masu gabatar da kara sun bukaci tabbatar da cewa Saipova ta kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ta yi musu lahani.
Bisa ga takardun kotu, ana tsammanin hukuncin kisa ya kamata a yanke.
Makonni bayan harin, babban kotun tarayya ya yanke hukuncin da ya zargi Saipov da laifin aikata laifuka 22 da suka hada da aikata laifuka masu yawa da ake amfani da su a kotu, da cin zarafi da kuma lalata motoci, da kuma kisan mutane takwas da ya yi da manufar ta'addanci.
Mai gabatar da kara ya ce harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da aka yi a hankali" kuma ya bayyana ayyukan Saipov a matsayin "abin ƙyama, zalunci da lalata".
"Saipov Saifullo Habibullayevich ya haifar da rauni da raunin da ya faru, ya kashe dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Anne-Lora Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlee, Ernan Ferrucci, Ernan Diego Mendoz da Alejandro Damián Pagnocco".
Biyar daga cikin mutanen da suka mutu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma ke nan da aka yi kisa a gundumar New York ta Kudu.
An tuhumi wanda ake tuhuma Khalid Barnes da laifin kashe wasu 'yan kasuwa biyu na miyagun ƙwayoyi, amma a watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009, an yanke masa hukuncin ɗaurin rai da rai.
A wani shari'a da aka yi a New York, an kashe ma'aurata Julius da Ethel Rosenberg a shekara ta 1953 domin sun yi alkawarin yin leƙen asiri a lokacin da ake Yaƙin Cacar Baki da Soviet Union.
An kashe Rosenberg da matarsa a kan kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun kotu, Saipov, dan kasar Uzbekistan, bai yi nadamar abin da ya aikata ba, kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce mutumin ya ce bai yi nadamar abin da ya yi ba.
A cewar tuhumar, bidiyon ISIS a wayar Saipov ne ya sa aka kai harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya nemi a saka tutar ISIS a asibitin.
Ya ƙi yarda da zargin da ake yi masa a ƙarƙashin Mataki na 22.
David Patton, wani lauya na zamantakewar jama'a, wanda ke kare Saipov, ya ce "mun yi matukar takaici" da hukuncin da ofishin lauya ya yanke.
Patton ya ce, "Hukunci na mutuwa ne kawai zai kara wa wadanda abin ya shafa rauni, ba ɗaurin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba".
A lokacin, lauyoyin Saipov sun nemi kotu ta dakatar da hukuncin kisa.
