Nancy Pelosi ta kira Brett Kavanaugh "mai cin abinci mai cin abinci" kuma ta ce ba shi da cancanta ya yi aiki a Kotun Koli
Shugabar jam'iyyar 'yancin mata Nancy Pelosi ta kira dan takarar Kotun Koli na kasar Burt Kavanaugh "mai tsananin damuwa" wanda ya ce ba shi da inganci don Kotun Koli.
Pelosi ta yi magana game da wannan a wata hira da aka yi da ita a ranar Asabar a Texas Tribune Festival a Austin, Texas.
"Idan mace ta yi haka, ina ganin za su ce tana da tsananin damuwa", in ji Pelosi game da Kavanaugh a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa a ranar Alhamis.
Kavanaugh ta musanta zargin da aka yi mata cewa ta yi wa Dr. Christine Blasey Ford fyaɗe sa'ad da take matashiya.
Kawano ya yi ihu sosai a lokacin jawabinsa, yana magana game da iyalinsa da kuma lokacin da yake makarantar sakandare, yana numfashi a hankali kuma yana da motsin rai.
Ya kuma zargi 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat a kwamitin da "kisan kai da aka yi da gangan" da 'yan sassaucin ra'ayi suka shirya a kan Hillary Clinton, wanda ya yi fushi da rashin nasarar zaben shugaban kasa na 2016.
A lokacin da aka tambaye ta game da Kavanaugh, Pelosi ta ce ta nuna cewa tana da ra'ayi na Democrat kuma ta tabbatar da cewa ba ta da damar zama a Kotun Koli.
"Ina ganin wannan jawabin da ya yi game da Clinton da 'yan Democrat ya zama rashin cancanta", in ji ta.
Pelosi ta damu sosai game da ko za a iya tuhumar Kavanaugh idan an tabbatar da laifinsa kuma idan 'yan Democrat sun sami rinjaye a majalisar wakilai.
