Sabuntawa a kan Red Fusion: Ragewa a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Wani rahoto daga Hukumar Kifi da Daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa an samu raguwar ruwan sama a yankin Tampa Bay.
Hukumar ta ce, an yi zargin cewa akwai ciwon daji a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte, da Collier.
Ƙarƙashin Red ya kai kusan mil 130 (209.21 km) daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin Lee.
An kuma ga irin wannan a cikin nisan mil 10 daga Hillsboro, amma ba su da yawa kamar yadda suka yi a makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga wannan a yankin Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an samu matsakaitan ƙwayoyin cuta a yankin Pinellas da kewayenta, kuma daga ƙananan zuwa manyan ƙwayoyin cuta a yankin Hillsborough, mafi girma a yankin Manatee, mafi girma a Sarasota ko bakin teku kusa da shi, matsakaici a Charlotte, mafi girma a yankin Lee da kewayenta, kuma mafi ƙarancin a Collier.
Har ila yau, mutane da yawa suna fama da rashin lafiyar numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da Collier.
Ba a samu wani ciwo na rashin lafiyar numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba a makon da ya gabata.
